4 “(2)(a) ‘Beneficiary’ means an injured worker, and the spouse in a marriage, child or dependent
5 of a worker, who is entitled to receive payments under this chapter.
6 “(b) ‘Beneficiary’ does not include a person who intentionally causes the compensable injury to
7 or death of an injured worker.
